metadata.description:
Bianca Leonor Quiñones also known as QUIN is an independent multifaceted creator and musician based in Los Angeles. QUIN began by sharing her music through a style she describes as “Fantasy Soul” -A self made genre intended to showcase the power of boundless versatility through sound. Since then, Fantasy Soul has evolved into a world full of different creative mediums, events and experiences through the imagination of QUIN. 

*Thinkin Bout You II is a reimagined version of my original Thinkin Bout You Soundcloud release from 2015. My songs are often an open dialogue between me and my Highest Self. This is a love letter to me, a calling home after straying away too long; a conversation about dreaming my way back to Self.  

<3 Q

lyrics.text:
Lyin on the front lawn
I got all these questions for ya
i just need an answer 
just tell me how long I gotta wait up for ya

I gotta know, 
do you think about me
Yeah, I gotta know
cuz I’ve been thinkin bout you all damn day 

You know that I need you
but you know that you need me too
Impossible to read you
but you know that you need me too 

Now we’re lyin on the front lawn
What if I said I’ll run away with ya
Babe you know that we can go to dreamland
Just tell me how long I gotta wait up for ya
<3 Q
